{"word":"τυκτός","slug":"τυκτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105842\" key=\"tukto/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τυκτός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">τεύχω</etym>) <sense id=\"n105842.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">finished, wrought out,</tr_> i. e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">complete,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τυκτὸν κακόν,</foreign> of Ares, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:831\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.831</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρήνη τυκτή</foreign> a fountain <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">made by man's hand,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:206\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.206</biblScope> </bibl>: then, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">well-made, well-wrought,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τυκτῇσι βόεσσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:105\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.105</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of a bowling-green, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν τ. δαπέδῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:627\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.627</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.169</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τυκτὴ μάρμαρος,</foreign> of a tombstone, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:210\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.210</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}